return ['domain'=>'capability-manager-enhanced','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','language'=>'yor','project-id-version'=>'PublishPress Capabilities 2.40.0','pot-creation-date'=>'2026-03-23T21:48:55+00:00','po-revision-date'=>'2026-04-22 08:34+0000','x-generator'=>'Loco https://localise.biz/','messages'=>['PublishPress Capabilities'=>'Awọn agbara PublishPress','https://publishpress.com/capability-manager/'=>'https://publishpress.com/capability-manager/','PublishPress Capabilities is the access control plugin for WordPress. You can manage all your WordPress user roles, from Administrators to Subscribers.'=>'Awọn agbara PublishPress jẹ ohun itanna iṣakoso iraye si fun WordPress. O le ṣakoso gbogbo awọn ipa olumulo WordPress rẹ, lati awọn alakoso si awọn alabapin.','PublishPress'=>'PublishPress','https://publishpress.com/'=>'https://publishpress.com/','%1s Error: %2s  PublishPress Capabilities cannot function because another copy of the plugin is active.'=>'%1s Aṣiṣe: %2s  Awọn Agbara PublishPress ko le ṣiṣẹ nitori ẹda miiran ti plugin naa ti wa ni iṣẹ.','This plugin can be deleted.'=>'A lè pa plugin yìí run.','You can block pages by URL or hide Admin elements by entering a CSS class or ID. This feature is available in PublishPress Capabilities Pro.'=>'O le dènà awọn oju-iwe nipasẹ URL tabi pa awọn eroja Alakoso mọ nipa titẹ kilasi CSS tabi ID. Iṣẹ yii wa ni PublishPress Capabilities Pro.','Upgrade to Pro'=>'Gbadun si Pro','Admin Menu Restrictions'=>'Iwọn Didara Akọkọ Alakoso','You can restrict access to admin menu screens. You can also edit, change, add, or remove links from the WordPress admin menu. This feature is available in PublishPress Capabilities Pro.'=>'O le dènà iraye si awọn iboju akojọ alakoso. O tun le satunkọ, yi, fi, tabi yọ awọn ọna asopọ kuro ni akojọ alakoso WordPress. Iṣẹ yii wa ni PublishPress Capabilities Pro.','You\'re using PublishPress Capabilities Free. The Pro version has more features and support. %sUpgrade to Pro%s'=>'Iwọ nlo PublishPress Capabilities Free. Ẹya Pro ni awọn ẹya diẹ sii ati atilẹyin. %sGbadun si Pro%s','Admin Menus'=>'Awọn akojọ aṣayan Alakoso','Hide CSS Elements'=>'Pa awọn eroja CSS mọ','Block by URL'=>'Dena nipasẹ URL','Admin Menus allows you to edit the admin menu links and control who has access.'=>'Awọn akojọ aṣayan iṣakoso gba ọ laaye lati ṣe atunṣe awọn ọna asopọ akojọ aṣayan iṣakoso ati ṣakoso ẹni ti o ni iraye si.','Select pages...'=>'Yan awọn oju-iwe...','You can select page types where this element will be added.'=>'O le yan awọn iru oju-iwe nibiti a yoo fi nkan yii kun.','Metaboxes'=>'Àwọn Metaboxes','Checklist'=>'Atokọ ayẹwo','Editorial Comments'=>'Awọn Ọrọ Akomọ','Notifications'=>'Ìkìlọ̀','TaxoPress - Settings'=>'TaxoPress - Eto','You can hide plugin metaboxes. You can also hide specific items by entering their CSS class or ID. This feature is available in PublishPress Capabilities Pro.'=>'O le pa awọn metaboxes plugin mọ. O tun le pa awọn nkan kan mọ nipa titẹ kilasi CSS tabi ID wọn. Iṣẹ yii wa ni PublishPress Capabilities Pro.','Custom Items'=>'Awọn nkan adani','Custom item one'=>'Ohun kan adani kan','Permalink: Descriptive Caption'=>'Permalink: Apejuwe Apejuwe','Page Attributes: Order'=>'Àwọn Àmì Ojú-iwe: Àtòjọ','You can use Frontend Features to target specific posts and pages. This feature is available in PublishPress Capabilities Pro.'=>'O le lo Awọn ẹya Frontend lati dojukọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ ati awọn oju-iwe pato. Iṣẹ yii wa ni PublishPress Capabilities Pro.','Select post types...'=>'Yan awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ...','This will add a metabox on the post editing screen. You can use this feature to add body classes only for that post.'=>'Eyi yóò fi metabox kun lori iboju ṣiṣatunkọ ìkànnì. O le lo iṣẹ́ yìí láti fi kilasi ara kun fún ìkànnì yẹn nìkan.','Drag multiple roles selection to change roles order.'=>'Fa yiyan awọn iṣẹ pupọ lati yi aṣẹ awọn iṣẹ pada.','Page title'=>'Akọle oju-iwe','Rank Math SEO'=>'Rank Math SEO','Capabilities'=>'Awọn agbara','No permission!'=>'Kò sí àṣẹ!','Invalid nonce token!'=>'Aami nonce ti ko tọ!','Error: wrong data'=>'Aṣiṣe: data ti ko tọ','An error occured!'=>'Aṣiṣe kan ṣẹlẹ!','Security check failed'=>'Ayẹwo aabo kuna','Permission denied'=>'Iṣẹ-iyọọda ti kọ','Settings updated successfully.'=>'Awọn iṣeto ti ni imudojuiwọn ni aṣeyọri.','Logged In Users'=>'Àwọn Olùmúlò Tí a Wọlé','Logged Out Users'=>'Àwọn Olùmúlò Tí a Sọkalẹ','PublishPress Capabilities Menu Restriction'=>'Ìdènà akojọ PublishPress','This menu is restricted for the following roles'=>'Àkójọ yìí ni a dènà fún awọn ipa wọnyi','Dashboard'=>'Iboju iṣakoso','Roles'=>'Awọn Iṣẹ','Settings'=>'Awọn iṣeto','Success notices'=>'Ìkìlọ̀ aṣeyọrí','Error notices'=>'Awọn akiyesi aṣiṣe','Warning notices'=>'Ìkìlọ̀ ìkìlọ̀','Info notices'=>'Awọn ifitonileti alaye','Current Role'=>'Ipo Tẹ́lẹ̀','Admin Notices'=>'Awọn Ikilọ Iṣakoso','Save for all Roles'=>'Fipamọ fun gbogbo Awọn Iṣẹ','Save for %s'=>'Fipamọ fun %s','Notification center access'=>'Ibi ìkìlọ̀ ìfọwọ́lé','Enable %1$s access to the Admin Notices area.'=>'Mú %1$s wọlé sí àgbègbè Àwọn Ìkìlọ̀ Aládàáṣiṣẹ́.','Notifications to remove from WordPress admin pages'=>'Ìkìlọ̀ láti yọ kúrò ní ojúewé olùdarí WordPress','Select the notification types that should be hidden when a user in the %1$s role is viewing WordPress admin screens.'=>'Yan àwọn irú ìkìlọ̀ tí yóò yẹ kó parẹ́ nígbà tí oníṣe kan nínú ipo %1$s bá ń wo àwọn iboju àlàáfíà WordPress.','Click here for more on notice types.'=>'Tẹ nibi fun diẹ sii lori awọn iru akiyesi.','Notifications to display in the Admin Notices area.'=>'Ìkìlọ̀ láti fi hàn nínú àgbègbè Ìkìlọ̀ Olùdarí.','Select the notification types that should be displayed in the Admin Notices area after been removed from the WordPress admin screens.'=>'Yan awọn iru ikilọ ti o yẹ ki o han ni agbegbe Awọn Ikilọ Alakoso lẹhin ti a yọ wọn kuro ninu awọn iboju alakoso WordPress.','Admin Notices allows you to clean up the WordPress admin area by organizing extra messages and advertisements into one place.'=>'Àwọn Ìkìlọ̀ Aládàáṣiṣẹ́ gba ọ laaye láti mọ́ àgbègbè àlàáfíà WordPress rẹ nípa ṣiṣàtúnṣe àwọn ìmessage tó pọ̀ jù lọ àti ìpolówó sí ibè kan.','Features include:'=>'Awọn ẹya-ara pẹlu:','Move selected notice types out of admin pages'=>'Gbe àwọn irú ìkìlọ̀ tí a yan kúrò ní àwọn ojúewé aládàáṣiṣẹ́','Show selected notices in a dedicated Admin Notices panel'=>'Fi àwọn ìkìlọ̀ tí a yan hàn nínú panẹli Àwọn Ìkìlọ̀ Aládàáṣiṣẹ́ tó yàtọ̀','Configure notice visibility by user role'=>'Ṣeto ìfarahàn ìkìlọ̀ nípa ipo oníṣe','View Documentation'=>'Wo Ìwé ìtọsọna','How to use Admin Notices'=>'Báwo ni a ṣe le lò Àwọn Ìkìlọ̀ Aládàáṣiṣẹ́','Display this notice'=>'Fihan ìkìlọ̀ yìí','Silence this notice'=>'Duro ìkìlọ̀ yìí','Hide this notice'=>'Pa ikilọ yii mọ','Move to Hidden Notices'=>'Gbe si Awọn Ifitonileti Ti a Pamọ','Displayed notices will no longer be removed from admin pages.'=>'Ìkìlọ̀ tí a fi hàn kò ní yọkuro mọ́ awọn oju-iwe alakoso.','This notice will be moved to the "Silenced Notices" tab and you will not receive a notification if it appears again.'=>'Ìkìlọ̀ yìí yóò lọ sí taabu "Awọn Ìkìlọ̀ Ti a Dẹ́kun" àti iwọ kò ní gba ìkìlọ̀ tí yóò bá hàn lẹ́ẹ̀kansi.','Hidden Notices'=>'Àwọn Ìkìlọ̀ tí a fi pamọ́','Silenced Notices'=>'Ìkìlọ̀ ti a dákẹ́','There are currently no admin notices.'=>'Kò sí ìkìlọ́ alákóso lọwọlọwọ.','Edit the settings.'=>'Ṣatunkọ awọn eto.','You do not have permission to manage admin notices.'=>'O ko ni igbanilaaye lati ṣakoso awọn akiyesi alakoso.','Invalid action. Reload this page and try again.'=>'Iṣe ti ko tọ. Tun ṣe igbasilẹ oju-iwe yii ki o si gbiyanju lẹẹkansii.','Invalid form.'=>'Fọọmu ti ko tọ.','Admin notice status updated successfully.'=>'Ipo akiyesi iṣakoso ti ni imudojuiwọn ni aṣeyọri.','Warning: This role cannot access the dashboard without the read capability. %1$sClick here to fix this now%2$s.'=>'Ìkìlọ̀: Iṣẹ́ yìí kò le wọlé sí dashboard láì ní agbára kika. %1$sTẹ nibi láti ṣatúnṣe eyi bayii%2$s.','Negate All'=>'Fagile Gbogbo','Negate None'=>'Fagile Ko si','Role Capabilities'=>'Agbara Iṣẹ','Search capabilities...'=>'Wa awọn agbara...','Nav Menus (Block)'=>'Akojọ Nav (Blok)','Block'=>'Dena','Nav Menus (Legacy)'=>'Akojọ Nav (Iṣẹ atijọ)','Legacy'=>'Iṣẹ́ àtijọ́','&nbsp;'=>'&nbsp;','Visibility'=>'Àfihàn','Editing'=>'Ṣatunkọ','Deletion'=>'Pipa','Taxonomies'=>'Taxonomies','Listing'=>'Ìtòkasí','Create Revision'=>'Ṣẹda Atunṣe','Submit Revision'=>'Firanṣẹ Atunṣe','Approve Revision'=>'Fọwọsi Atunṣe','Can read posts which are currently published with private visibility.'=>'Le ka awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade lọwọlọwọ pẹlu wiwo aladani.','Has basic editing capability (but may need other capabilities based on post status and ownership).'=>'Ni agbara ìtúnṣe ipilẹ (ṣùgbọ́n ó lè nílò awọn agbara míì gẹ́gẹ́ bí ipo ifiweranṣẹ ati ìní).','Can edit posts which were created by other users.'=>'Le satunkọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a ṣẹda nipasẹ awọn olumulo miiran.','Can edit posts which are currently published.'=>'Le satunkọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade lọwọlọwọ.','Can edit posts which are currently published with private visibility.'=>'Le satunkọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade lọwọlọwọ pẹlu wiwo aladani.','Can make a post publicly visible.'=>'Le ṣe ifiweranṣẹ naa han ni gbangba.','Has basic deletion capability (but may need other capabilities based on post status and ownership).'=>'Ni agbara ìparẹ́ ipilẹ (ṣùgbọ́n ó lè nílò awọn agbara míì gẹ́gẹ́ bí ipo ifiweranṣẹ ati ìní).','Can delete posts which were created by other users.'=>'Le paarẹ awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a ṣẹda nipasẹ awọn olumulo miiran.','Can delete posts which are currently published.'=>'Le paarẹ awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade lọwọlọwọ.','Can delete posts which are currently published with private visibility.'=>'Le paarẹ awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade lọwọlọwọ pẹlu wiwo aladani.','Multisite'=>'Multisite','Admin'=>'Alakoso','Invalid Capabilities'=>'Agbara ti ko tọ','Additional'=>'Afikun','Term %s Capabilities'=>'Iwọn %s Àwọn Agbara','%s Capabilities'=>'%s Awọn Agbara','Post %s Capabilities'=>'Agbara Ifiweranṣẹ %s','Taxonomy'=>'Taxonomy','Filter by taxonomy'=>'Ṣe àlẹmọ nípa taxonomy','Filter by post type'=>'Ṣawari nipasẹ iru ifiweranṣẹ','The slug for this taxonomy is %s'=>'Slug fún irú ìtẹ̀sí yìí ni %s','The slug for this post type is %s'=>'Slug fún irú ìkọ̀wé yìí ni %s','%s: assigned by Permission Group'=>'%s: ti yan nipasẹ Ẹgbẹ Àṣẹ','This capability is %s'=>'Àǹfààní yìí ni %s','This capability is controlled by %s'=>'Iṣẹ́ yìí ni a n ṣakoso nipasẹ %s','This capability is controlled by %s Use the sidebar settings to allow this to be controlled independently.'=>'Iṣẹ́ yìí ni a n ṣakoso nipasẹ %s Lo awọn eto ẹgbẹ́ ẹgbẹ́ lati jẹ́ kí a lè ṣakoso eyi lọ́tọ̀.','Use the sidebar settings to allow this to be controlled independently.'=>'Lo awọn eto sidebar lati gba eyi laaye lati ni iṣakoso ni ominira.','This capability is not available for this post type.'=>'Iṣẹ́ yìí kò sí fún irú ìkànnì yìí.','Admin listing access is normally provided by the "Edit" capabilities. These "List" capabilities only apply if the corresponding "Edit" capability is missing. Also, these "List" capabilities can grant access, but not deny access.'=>'Iwọle atokọ alakoso jẹ deede ni a pese nipasẹ awọn agbara "Ṣatunkọ". Awọn agbara "Atokọ" wọnyi kan lo nikan ti agbara "Ṣatunkọ" ti o ba wa ni ṣiṣi. Bakanna, awọn agbara "Atokọ" wọnyi le fun ni iwọle, ṣugbọn ko le kọ iwọle.','Filter by capability'=>'Ṣawari nipasẹ agbara','No results found. Please try again with a different word.'=>'Kò sí abajade tí a rí. Jọwọ gbìmọ̀ lẹ́ẹ̀kan síi pẹ̀lú ọ̀rọ̀ míràn.','check / uncheck all'=>'ṣayẹwo / yọ ayẹwo gbogbo','Capability Name'=>'Orukọ Agbara','WordPress Core Capabilities'=>'Àwọn Agbara WordPress Core','General'=>'Gbogbogbo','Plugin Capabilities &ndash; %s'=>'Agbara Plugin &ndash; %s','The User Testing feature also requires the %1$s edit_users %2$s capability.'=>'Ẹ̀ka Iṣẹ́ Ìdánwò Olùsọdá náà tún nilo àǹfààní %1$s edit_users %2$s.','The following entries have no effect. Please assign desired capabilities on the Editing / Deletion / Private tabs.'=>'Àwọn ìforúkọsílẹ̀ tó tẹ̀le yìí kò ní ipa. Jọ̀wọ́ yàn àwọn àǹfààní tí a fẹ́ ní àwọn taabu Àtúnṣe / Pipa / Àkọsílẹ̀.','Additional Capabilities'=>'Afikun Agbara','You have no additional capabilities.'=>'Iwọ ko ni awọn agbara afikun.','Capabilities allows you change the permissions for any user role.'=>'Awọn agbara gba ọ laaye lati yi awọn igbanilaaye fun eyikeyi ipa olumulo.','%1$s = Capability granted %2$s'=>'%1$s = Agbara ti fun %2$s','usage key'=>'bọtini lilo','%1$s = Capability not granted %2$s'=>'%1$s = Agbara ti ko fun %2$s','%1$s = Capability denied, even if granted by another role %2$s'=>'%1$s = Agbara ti kọ, paapaa ti a ba fun ni nipasẹ ipa miiran %2$s','You can also configure this role as a %sPermission Group%s.'=>'O tun le tunto ipa yii gẹgẹbi %sIgbẹkẹle Ẹgbẹ%s.','How to use Capabilities'=>'Bawo ni lati lo Awọn agbara','Capabilities is Safe to Use'=>'Awọn agbara jẹ Ailewu lati Lo','WordPress stores role capabilities in your database, where they remain even if the plugin is deactivated.'=>'WordPress tọju awọn agbara ipa ninu ibi ipamọ data rẹ, nibiti wọn ti wa paapaa ti a ba mu plugin naa kuro.','Whenever you use PublishPress Capabilities to save changes, it also creates a backup which you can use to restore a previous configuration.'=>'Nigba tí o ba n lo PublishPress Capabilities lati fipamọ́ àwọn ayipada, o tun dá àtúnṣe kan silẹ tí o le lo lati túnṣe iṣeto àtẹ́yẹ rẹ.','Go to the Backup feature'=>'Lọ sí ẹya Backup','Add a New Capability'=>'Ṣe afikun Agbara Tuntun','Add to role'=>'Fi kun si ipa','New capabilities are controlled on the Additonal tab.'=>'Awọn agbara tuntun ni a n ṣakoso lori taabu afikun.','PublishPress Permissions'=>'Awọn igbanilaaye PublishPress','Automatically define type-specific capabilities for your custom post types and taxonomies'=>'Ṣe idanimọ awọn agbara pato-iru laifọwọyi fun awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ adani rẹ ati awọn ẹka','Assign standard WP roles supplementally for a specific post type'=>'Yọọda awọn ipa WP boṣewa pọ si fun iru ifiweranṣẹ pato','Assign custom WP roles supplementally for a specific post type <em>(Pro)</em>'=>'Yọọda awọn ipa WP adani pọ si fun iru ifiweranṣẹ pato <em>(Pro)</em>','Customize reading permissions per-category or per-post'=>'Ṣatunkọ awọn aṣẹ kika ni ibamu si ẹka tabi ni ibamu si ifiweranṣẹ','Customize editing permissions per-category or per-post <em>(Pro)</em>'=>'Ṣatunkọ awọn aṣẹ ṣiṣe ni ibamu si ẹka tabi ni ibamu si ifiweranṣẹ <em>(Pro)</em>','Custom Post Visibility statuses, fully implemented throughout wp-admin <em>(Pro)</em>'=>'Ipo ifihan ifiweranṣẹ adani, ti a ṣe imuse ni gbogbo wp-admin <em>(Pro)</em>','Custom Moderation statuses for access-controlled, multi-step publishing workflow <em>(Pro)</em>'=>'Ipo iṣakoso adani fun awọn iṣẹ ṣiṣe atẹjade ti a ṣe akoso, multi-step <em>(Pro)</em>','Regulate permissions for Edit Flow post statuses <em>(Pro)</em>'=>'Ṣakoso awọn igbanilaaye fun awọn ipo Ifiweranṣẹ Edit Flow <em>(Pro)</em>','Customize the moderated editing of published content with Revisionary or Post Forking <em>(Pro)</em>'=>'Ṣatunkọ iṣakoso ti akoonu ti a tẹjade pẹlu Revisionary tabi Post Forking <em>(Pro)</em>','Grant Spectator, Participant or Moderator access to specific bbPress forums <em>(Pro)</em>'=>'Fún àyè wọlé si Spectator, Participant tàbí Moderator ní àwọn forum bbPress pàtó <em>(Pro)</em>','Grant supplemental content permissions to a BuddyPress group <em>(Pro)</em>'=>'Fún àyè ìmúlò akoonu àfikún sí ẹgbẹ́ BuddyPress <em>(Pro)</em>','WPML integration to mirror permissions to translations <em>(Pro)</em>'=>'Iṣọpọ WPML lati ṣe afihan awọn igbanilaaye si awọn itumọ <em>(Pro)</em>','Member support forum'=>'Àwọn forum ìtùnú ọmọ ẹgbẹ́','%1$sgrab%2$s %3$s'=>'%1$sgrab%2$s %3$s','%s (free install)'=>'%s (fifi sori ọfẹ)','%1$sbuy%2$s %3$s'=>'%1$sbuy%2$s %3$s','%s info/purchase'=>'%s alaye/ra','Role level is mostly deprecated. However, it still determines eligibility for Post Author assignment and limits the application of user editing capabilities.'=>'Ipele iṣẹ ti wa ni afikun pupọ. Sibẹsibẹ, o tun pinnu ifarada fun ipin akọwe Post ati pe o ni ihamọ lori lilo awọn agbara ṣiṣatunkọ olumulo.','Level:'=>'Ìpele:','Create this role definition in new (future) sites'=>'Ṣẹda itumọ ẹka yii ni awọn aaye tuntun (ti mbọ)','Include in new sites.'=>'Pẹlu ni awọn aaye tuntun.','Copy / update this role definition to all sites now'=>'Daakọ / ṣe imudojuiwọn itumọ ipa yii si gbogbo awọn aaye bayi','Sync role to all sites.'=>'Sínkù ipa sí gbogbo awọn aaye.','Copy option settings to all sites now'=>'Da awọn eto aṣayan si gbogbo awọn aaye bayi','Sync options to all sites.'=>'Sínkù àwọn aṣayan sí gbogbo awọn aaye.','You do not have permission to restore backup.'=>'Iwọ ko ni aṣẹ lati tun gbe afẹyinti pada.','New backup saved.'=>'Atilẹba tuntun ti fipamọ.','Roles and Capabilities restored from initial backup.'=>'Awọn Iṣẹ ati Agbara ti da duro lati afẹyinti ibẹrẹ.','Restore failed. No backup found.'=>'Múpadà kuna. Ko si afẹyinti ti a ri.','%s restored from last backup.'=>'%s ti da pada lati afẹyinti to kẹhin.','Roles and Capabilities restored from selected auto-backup.'=>'Awọn Iṣẹ ati Agbara ti da duro lati afẹyinti aiyipada ti a yan.','Please upload a file to import'=>'Jọwọ gbe faili kan lati gbe wọle','Please upload a valid .json file'=>'Jọwọ gbe faili .json to wulo wọle','Error importing settings! Please try again.'=>'Aṣiṣe ni gbigbe awọn eto! Jọwọ tun gbiyanju.','Error importing settings! Please check that you uploaded a valid json file.'=>'Aṣiṣe ni gbigbe awọn eto! Jọwọ ṣayẹwo pe o gbe faili json to tọ.','%s successfully imported from uploaded data.'=>'%s ti wọle ni aṣeyọri lati data ti a gbe.','Needed function to create default roles not found!'=>'Iṣẹ ti a nilo lati ṣẹda awọn ipa aiyipada ko ri!','Roles and Capabilities reset to WordPress defaults'=>'Awọn Iṣẹ ati Agbara ti tun pada si awọn aiyipada WordPress','Backup Tool for PublishPress Capabilities'=>'Igbẹkẹle Ọpa fun Awọn Agbara PublishPress','Restore'=>'Múpadà','Backup'=>'Igbẹkẹle','Reset Roles'=>'Tun Roles ṣe','Export / Import'=>'Gbe jade / Gbe wọle','Backup Roles and Capabilities'=>'Igbẹkẹle Awọn ipa ati Agbara','PublishPress Capabilities automatically creates a backup on installation and whenever you save changes. The initial backup and last %d auto-backups are kept.'=>'Awọn agbara PublishPress ṣẹda afẹyinti laifọwọyi lori fifi sori ati nigbakugba ti o ba fipamọ awọn ayipada. Afẹyinti ibẹrẹ ati awọn afẹyinti %d to kẹhin ni a pa.','A backup created on this screen replaces any previous manual backups, but is never automatically replaced.'=>'Afẹyinti kan ti a ṣẹda lori iboju yii rọpo eyikeyi afẹyinti ọwọ ti tẹlẹ, ṣugbọn kii yoo rọpo laifọwọyi.','Manual Backup'=>'Àtúnṣe Ikọkọ','Last Manual Backup - %s'=>'Àtúnṣe Ikọkọ Ikẹhin - %s','Last Backup'=>'Iboju-aye Ikẹhin','Restore Previous Roles and Capabilities'=>'Múpadà awọn Roles ati Agbara ti tẹlẹ','PublishPress Capabilities automatically creates a backup on installation and whenever you save changes.'=>'Awọn agbara PublishPress ṣẹda afẹyinti laifọwọyi lori fifi sori ati nigbakugba ti o ba fipamọ awọn ayipada.','On this screen, you can restore an earlier version of your roles and capabilities.'=>'Nínú iboju yìí, o le tún àtúnṣe àtijọ́ ti àwọn ipa rẹ àti agbára rẹ padà.','Available Backups:'=>'Awọn Igbẹkẹle Ti o wa:','all roles'=>'gbogbo awọn ipa','Manual backup of %s (%s)'=>'Àtúnṣe ikọkọ ti %s (%s)','Auto-backup of all roles (%s)'=>'Igbẹkẹle adaṣe ti gbogbo awọn ipa (%s)','Initial backup of all roles'=>'Iboju-aye akọkọ ti gbogbo awọn ipa','Restore Selected Roles'=>'Múpadà awọn Roles ti a yan','Show changes from current roles only'=>'Fi awọn ayipada lati awọn ipa lọwọlọwọ nikan han','Initial Backup - %s'=>'Iboju-aye Ipilẹṣẹ - %s','Initial Backup'=>'Iboju-aye Ipilẹṣẹ','%s (%s roles)'=>'%s (%s awọn ipa)','(this role will be removed if you restore backup)'=>'(ipa yii yoo yọkuro ti o ba da afẹyinti pada)','%s (level %s)'=>'%s ( ipele %s)','No changes'=>'Kò sí àtúnṣe','Reset WordPress Defaults'=>'Tun awọn aiyipada WordPress ṣe','Warning:'=>'Ìkìlọ̀:','Reseting default Roles and Capabilities will set them to the WordPress install defaults.'=>'Tun awọn Roles ati Agbara aiyipada ṣe yoo ṣeto wọn si awọn aiyipada fifi sori WordPress.','If you have installed any plugin that adds new roles or capabilities, these will be lost.'=>'Ti o ba ti fi sori ẹrọ eyikeyi ohun afikun ti o nfi awọn ipa tuntun tabi awọn agbara kun, iwọnyi yoo sọnu.','It is recommended to use this only as a last resource!'=>'A ṣe iṣeduro lati lo eyi nikan bi orisun ikẹhin!','Reset Roles and Capabilities to WordPress defaults'=>'Tun Roles ati Agbara ṣe si awọn aiyipada WordPress','You are about to reset Roles and Capabilities to WordPress defaults.
 \'Cancel\' to stop, \'OK\' to reset.'=>'O ti wa ni setan lati tun Roles ati Capabilities si awọn aiyipada WordPress. \'Fagile\' lati da duro, \'OK\' lati tunṣe.','Reset to WordPress defaults'=>'Tun ṣe si awọn aiyipada WordPress','Export Settings'=>'Gbe jade Awọn eto','Export the plugin settings for this site as a .json file. This allows you to easily import the configuration into another site.'=>'Gbe awọn eto plugin fun aaye yii jade gẹgẹbi faili .json. Eyi n jẹ ki o rọrun lati gbe iṣeto naa wọle si aaye miiran.','Roles and Capabilities'=>'Awọn Iṣẹ ati Agbara','Export'=>'Gbe jade','Import Settings'=>'Gbigba Eto','Please make a \'Manual Backup\' in the backup tab to enable backup restore in case anything goes wrong.'=>'Jọwọ ṣe \'Afẹyinti Itọsọna\' ni taabu afẹyinti lati mu afẹyinti pada ti ohunkohun ba lọ ni aṣiṣe.','Import the plugin settings from a .json file. This file can be obtained by exporting the settings on another site using the form above.'=>'Gbigba awọn eto plugin lati faili .json. A le gba faili yii nipa gbigbe awọn eto lori aaye miiran nipa lilo fọọmu loke.','Before importing, we recommend using the "Backup" tab to create a backup of your current settings.'=>'Ṣaaju ki o to gbe wọle, a daba lati lo taabu "Igbẹkẹle" lati ṣẹda igbẹkẹle ti awọn eto rẹ lọwọlọwọ.','Admin Feature Restrictions'=>'Iwọn Didara Ohun Alakoso','Toggle all'=>'Yí gbogbo','Wildcard enabled'=>'Wildcard ti ṣiṣẹ́','URL targeted'=>'URL ti a fojusi','URL wildcard'=>'URL wildcard','Edit'=>'Ṣatunkọ','Admin Features allows you to remove elements from the admin area and toolbar.'=>'Awọn ẹya Alakoso gba ọ laaye lati yọ awọn eroja kuro ninu agbegbe alakoso ati toolbar.','No change'=>'Ko si iyipada','This feature is denied'=>'Ẹya yii ni a kọ','How to use Admin Features'=>'Bawo ni lati lo Awọn ẹya Admin','Admin Features Settings'=>'Iṣeto Awọn ẹya Alakoso','Hide Submenus'=>'Pa Awọn Submenus','Select a preset font family'=>'Yan ẹbi fọ́ntì tí a ti ṣètò','Custom style "%s" saved successfully.'=>'Aṣa ti a ṣe "%s" ti fipamọ ni aṣeyọri.','Custom style "%s" deleted successfully.'=>'Aṣa ti a ṣe "%s" ti paarẹ ni aṣeyọri.','Custom style name cannot be empty.'=>'Oruko aṣa ko le ṣofo.','Admin styles saved successfully.'=>'Awọn aṣa alakoso ti fipamọ ni aṣeyọri.','Admin Styles'=>'Awọn aṣa Iṣakoso','Setting'=>'Iṣeto','Value'=>'Iye','Admin Color Scheme'=>'Àwò Ọpọlọ Alakoso','Sets the admin color scheme for all users. Click a scheme to preview it instantly.'=>'Ṣeto awọ alakoso fun gbogbo awọn olumulo. Tẹ akọmọ kan lati ṣe afihan rẹ lẹsẹkẹsẹ.','Start from template'=>'Bẹrẹ lati àpẹẹrẹ','Blank Template'=>'Àpẹẹrẹ ofo','Add Custom Style'=>'Fi Aṣa ti a ṣe kun','Edit custom style'=>'Ṣatunkọ aṣa ti a ṣe','Edit Color Style'=>'Ṣatunkọ Aṣa Awọ','Customize colors for different admin elements. Changes are previewed instantly.'=>'Ṣatunkọ awọn awọ fun awọn eroja alakoso oriṣiriṣi. Awọn ayipada ni a ṣe afihan lẹsẹkẹsẹ.','Add more than one custom admin styles. This feature is available in PublishPress Capabilities Pro.'=>'Ṣe afikun ju aṣa admin ọkan lọ. Ẹya yii wa ni PublishPress Capabilities Pro.','Add CSS selectors (class or ID), choose a style variation, and set a brand color.'=>'Fi awọn aṣayan CSS kun (kilasi tabi ID), yan iyatọ aṣa, ki o si ṣeto awọ ami kan.','Add New Element'=>'Fi Ẹrọ Tuntun kun','Selector'=>'Aṣayan','e.g. .publishpress-wrap h1, #my-plugin-header'=>'f.i. .publishpress-wrap h1, #my-plugin-header','Variation'=>'Iyatọ','Background'=>'Abẹ́rẹ́','Text'=>'Ìkọ́','Border'=>'Ààlà','Brand Color'=>'Àwọ́ Àami','Remove'=>'Yọ','Custom Style Name'=>'Orúkọ Àṣà Tó Yàtọ̀','e.g., Company Branding, Dark Mode'=>'àpẹẹrẹ, Àmì Ilé-iṣẹ́, Ìmọ́ Dudu','Cancel'=>'Fagilee','Delete Custom Style'=>'Pa Àṣà Tó Yàtọ̀','Are you sure you want to delete this %1s? %2s %3s'=>'Ṣé o dájú pé o fẹ́ pa %1s yìí? %2s %3s','Custom Style'=>'Àṣà Tó Yàtọ̀','Save Custom Style'=>'Fipamọ́ Àṣà Tó Yàtọ̀','Custom Admin Logo'=>'Aami Alakoso Adani','Upload a custom logo to replace the WordPress icon in the admin bar. Recommended: 20px by 20px in SVG or PNG format.'=>'Gba aami aṣa kan silẹ lati rọpo aami WordPress ninu ọpa alakoso. A ṣe iṣeduro: 20px nipasẹ 20px ni ọna kika SVG tabi PNG.','Select Image'=>'Yan Aworan','Custom Favicon'=>'Favicon Adani','Upload a custom favicon for the admin area. Recommended: 16px by 16px or 32px by 32px in SVG or PNG format.'=>'Gba aworan favicon aṣa kan silẹ fun agbegbe alakoso. A ṣe iṣeduro: 16px nipasẹ 16px tabi 32px nipasẹ 32px ni ọna kika SVG tabi PNG.','Admin Font Family'=>'Ẹbi Fọ́ntì Aládàáṣiṣẹ́','Set a font stack for the admin area, for example "Segoe UI", sans-serif.'=>'Ṣeto akojọpọ fọ́ntì fún àgbègbè aládàáṣiṣẹ́, fún àpẹẹrẹ "Segoe UI", sans-serif.','Preset Fonts'=>'Fọ́ntì Tí a Ti Ṣètò','Custom Value'=>'Iye Àdáni','Admin Font Size'=>'Iwọn Fọ́ntì Aládàáṣiṣẹ́','Set a base font size for the admin area. Leave empty to use the default WordPress size.'=>'Ṣeto iwọn fọ́ntì ipilẹ fún àgbègbè aládàáṣiṣẹ́. Fi silẹ́ kí o lo iwọn WordPress tó jẹ́ àtọkànwá.','Default'=>'Igbasilẹ','Named Sizes'=>'Iwọn orukọ','Pixel Sizes'=>'Iwọn piksẹli','Typography Overrides'=>'Àtúnṣe Typography','Optional target-specific typography rules for common admin elements.'=>'Àwọn òfin typography tó jẹ́ àṣàyàn fún àwọn eroja aládàáṣiṣẹ́ wọpọ.','Body Text'=>'Ìtẹ́tẹ́ Ara','Links'=>'Awọn ọna asopọ','Headings'=>'Àkọlé','Admin Menu'=>'Àtẹ̀jáde Àṣẹ','Admin Bar'=>'Ibi iṣakoso','Form Fields'=>'Àwọn Pẹpẹ Fọ́ọ̀mù','Buttons'=>'Bọtìn','Target'=>'Ero','Font Family'=>'Ibi Fonti','Font Size'=>'Iwọn fọnti','Preset'=>'Preset','Custom'=>'Adani','Admin Footer Text'=>'Ọrọ-ẹgbẹ Alakoso','Replace the default "Thanks for creating with WordPress" message in the admin footer.'=>'Rọpo ifiranṣẹ aiyipada "O ṣeun fun ṣiṣẹda pẹlu WordPress" ninu ẹsẹ alakoso.','Replace "Howdy"'=>'Rọpo "Bawo ni"','Replace "Howdy" in the admin bar.'=>'Rọpo "Bawo ni" ninu ọpa alakoso.','Control Settings'=>'Awọn Eto iṣakoso','Control how admin styles are applied to users.'=>'Ṣakoso bi awọn aṣa alakoso ṣe n ni ipa lori awọn olumulo.','Hide Admin Color Scheme settings in user profile'=>'Pa awọn eto awọ Admin mọ ni profaili olumulo','When enabled, users cannot see or change color scheme settings in their profile. Role-based settings will be applied.'=>'Nígbà tí a bá ṣiṣẹ́, awọn olumulo kò le rí tàbí yí ìtọ́sọ́nà awọ yíyí pada nínú profaili wọn. Àwọn ìtọ́sọ́nà ti a da lori iṣẹ́ ni yóò wulo.','Force role settings (override user selection)'=>'Forukọsilẹ awọn eto ipa (pàdé yiyan olumulo)','When enabled, role settings will always apply, overriding any user selection even if the color scheme UI is visible to them.'=>'Nígbà tí a bá ṣiṣẹ́, ìtọ́sọ́nà iṣẹ́ yóò ma lo, tí yóò kọ́ gbogbo yiyan olumulo kó dùn mọ́ wọn.','Admin Styles allows you to customize the WordPress admin area with your own branding.'=>'Awọn aṣa Iṣakoso gba ọ laaye lati ṣe akanṣe agbegbe iṣakoso WordPress pẹlu ami iyasọtọ tirẹ.','Custom admin color schemes'=>'Awọn awọ aṣa alakoso','Replace the WordPress logo and favicon'=>'Rọpo aami WordPress ati favicon','Custom footer text'=>'Iwe afọwọkọ adani','Replace "Howdy" text'=>'Rọpo ọrọ "Bawo ni"','How to use Admin Styles'=>'Bawo ni lati lo Awọn ara Admin','Security check failed.'=>'Ayẹwo aabo kuna.','You do not have permission to manage admin styles.'=>'O ko ni igbanilaaye lati ṣakoso awọn aṣa alakoso.','No role specified.'=>'Kò sí ipa tí a sọtọ.','Use this Image'=>'Lò Àwòrán yìí','Saving...'=>'Nítorí pé a n fipamọ́...','Settings saved.'=>'Àwọn ìṣètò ti fipamọ́.','Current logo preview'=>'Àwòrán àfihàn ààmì lọwọlọwọ','Add New Custom Style'=>'Fikun-un Àṣà Tó Yàtọ̀ Tuntun','Edit Custom Style'=>'Ṣatunkọ Àṣà Tó Yàtọ̀','Are you sure you want to delete "%s" custom style?'=>'Ṣé o dájú pé o fẹ́ pa àṣà tó yàtọ̀ "%s"?','this custom style'=>'àṣà tó yàtọ̀ yìí','Primary Button'=>'Bọtini Àkọ́kọ́','Hover State'=>'Ipo Iṣanlẹ̀','Notification'=>'Ìkìlọ̀','Live preview of your custom color scheme'=>'Àfihàn àtúnṣe ti àwọ̀ àdáni rẹ','Custom Style Name is required.'=>'Orukọ Àṣà àdáni jẹ́ dandan.','Main Admin Color is require