Post Attributes'=>'Awọn ohun-ini Ifiweranṣẹ','Block Panel'=>'Dena Panẹli','Paragraph'=>'Paragirafu','Typography'=>'Iru ọrọ','Color settings'=>'Awọn eto awọ','Text settings'=>'Àwọn eto ọrọ','This role is not enabled for profile feature editing.'=>'Ipa yìí kò sí fún ṣiṣatunkọ ẹya profaili.','An error occurred!'=>'Aṣiṣe kan ti ṣẹlẹ!','Profile features access disabled.'=>'Iwọle awọn ẹya profaili ti pa.','Invalid role provided.'=>'Ipa ti ko tọ ti a pese.','Profile features access enabled for this role.'=>'Iwọle awọn ẹya profaili ti muu ṣiṣẹ fun ipa yii.','Editor Features'=>'Awọn ẹya Akọwe','Admin Features'=>'Awọn ẹya Alakoso','Profile Features'=>'Awọn ẹya profaili','Redirects'=>'Awọn itọnisọna','Nav Menu'=>'Akojọ Nav','Roles allows you to create, edit, and delete all the user roles on your site.'=>'Awọn iṣẹ gba ọ laaye lati ṣẹda, ṣatunkọ, ati paarẹ gbogbo awọn ipa olumulo lori aaye rẹ.','Capabilities allows you to change the permissions for any user role.'=>'Awọn agbara gba ọ laaye lati yi awọn igbanilaaye fun eyikeyi ipa olumulo.','Admin Styles allows you to customize the admin area with your own branding.'=>'Awọn aṣa Iṣakoso gba ọ laaye lati ṣe akanṣe agbegbe iṣakoso pẹlu ami iyasọtọ tirẹ.','Redirects allows you to redirect users in a role after Registration, Login or Logout.'=>'Awọn itọnisọna n gba ọ laaye lati tọka awọn olumulo ni ipa lẹhin Iforukọsilẹ, Wọle tabi Jade.','Navigation Menus'=>'Awọn Akojọ Navigation','User Testing'=>'Ìdánwò Olumulo','Test your site by instantly logging in as another user. Available accounts include any which the current user can edit.'=>'Dáhùn aaye rẹ nipa ṣiṣi wọle lẹsẹkẹsẹ gẹgẹ bi olumulo miiran. Awọn iroyin ti o wa pẹlu eyikeyi ti olumulo ti lọwọlọwọ le ṣe atunṣe.','Remove Admin Notices from WordPress admin screen and organize them in to a single area.'=>'Yọ awọn Ifiranṣẹ Alakoso lati iboju alakoso WordPress ki o si ṣeto wọn sinu agbegbe kan.','Login permission denied.'=>'Ìjẹ́wọ́wọ́lé ti kọ.','You do not have permission to access this page.'=>'O ko ni igbanilaaye lati wọle si oju-iwe yii.','Need PublishPress Capabilities Support?'=>'Nilo Atilẹyin Awọn Agbara PublishPress?','If you need help or have a new feature request, let us know.'=>'Ti o ba nilo iranlọwọ tabi ti o ni ibeere ẹya tuntun, jẹ ki a mọ.','Request Support'=>'Beere atilẹyin','Detailed documentation is also available on the plugin website.'=>'Iwe aṣẹ alaye wa ni oju opo wẹẹbu afikun naa.','View Knowledge Base'=>'Wo Ilana Imọ','Social Links'=>'Awọn ọna asopọ Awujọ','Page Lists'=>'Àwọn Àkójọpọ̀ Ojú-iwe','New role created.'=>'Ipa tuntun ti a dá sílẹ̀.','Error: Failed creating the new role.'=>'Aṣiṣe: Kò ṣaṣeyọri lati ṣẹda ipa tuntun.','The selected role is not editable.'=>'Iṣẹ́ tí a yàn kò le ṣe àtúnṣe.','Incorrect capability name.'=>'Orukọ agbara ti ko tọ.','Type / Taxonomy settings saved.'=>'Iru / Awọn eto taxonomy ti fipamọ.','Bad form received.'=>'Fọọmu buburu ti gba.','You cannot remove Manage Capabilities from Administrators'=>'O ko le yọ iṣakoso Awọn agbara kuro lati ọdọ awọn Alakoso','This capability is explicitly negated. Click to add/remove normally.'=>'Iṣẹ́ yìí ti kọ́kọ́ jẹ́ kó ṣee ṣe. Tẹ láti fi kún/yọ́ nìkan.','Explicity negate this capability by storing as disabled'=>'Ni kedere kọ agbara yi nipa fipamọ bi a ti dènà','Explicitly negate these capabilities by storing as disabled'=>'Ni kedere kọ awọn agbara wọnyi nipa fipamọ bi a ti dènà','Post type registration does not define this capability distinctly'=>'Iforukọsilẹ iru ifiweranṣẹ ko ṣalaye agbara yii ni kedere','Add or remove this capability from the WordPress role'=>'Fi agbara yii kun tabi yọ kuro lati ipa WordPress','Add or remove capability from the role normally'=>'Fi agbara kun tabi yọ kuro lati ipa ni deede','Are you sure you want to delete this item ?'=>'Ṣe o dajudaju pe o fẹ pa nkan yii?','Add or clear custom item entry before saving changes.'=>'Fi ohun kan ti a ṣe adani kun tabi pa a run ki o to fipamọ awọn ayipada.','Role Name'=>'Orukọ Iṣẹ','Role Type'=>'Iru Iṣẹ','Default Role'=>'Iṣẹ Aiyipada','Admin Access'=>'Iwọle Alakoso','You do not have permission to manage roles.'=>'Iwọ ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣakoso awọn ipa.','You do not have permission to manage editor features.'=>'O ko ni igbanilaaye lati ṣakoso awọn ẹya olootu.','Settings updated.'=>'Awọn iṣeto ti ni imudojuiwọn.','You do not have permission to manage admin features.'=>'O ko ni igbanilaaye lati ṣakoso awọn ẹya alakoso.','You do not have permission to manage navigation menus.'=>'Iwọ ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣakoso awọn akojọ aṣayan lilọ.','You do not have permission to manage profile features.'=>'Iwọ ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣakoso awọn ẹya profaili.','You do not have permission to manage redirect.'=>'Iwọ ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣakoso atunṣe.','Invalid form. Reload this page and try again.'=>'Fọọmu ti ko tọ. Tun ṣe igbasilẹ oju-iwe yii ki o si gbiyanju lẹẹkansii.','You do not have permission to manage capabilities.'=>'O ko ni igbanilaaye lati ṣakoso awọn agbara.','New capability added to role.'=>'Agbara tuntun ti a fi kun si ipa.','Bad form Received'=>'Fọọmu buburu gba','You do not have permission to restore roles.'=>'Iwọ ko ni aṣẹ lati tun gbe awọn ipa pada.','You do not have permission to perform this action.'=>'Iwọ ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣe iṣe yii.','If you like %s, please leave us a %s rating. Thank you!'=>'Ti o ba fẹ %s, jọwọ fi %s iwọn silẹ fun wa. O ṣeun!','About PublishPress Capabilities'=>'Nipa Awọn agbara PublishPress','About'=>'Nipa','Capabilites Documentation'=>'Iwe Itọsọna Awọn agbara','Documentation'=>'Iwe aṣẹ','Contact the PublishPress team'=>'Kan si ẹgbẹ PublishPress','Contact'=>'Kan si','Permissions & Access'=>'Aṣẹ & Wiwọle','Administer advanced content permissions and visibility rules.'=>'Sọ awọn aṣẹ akoonu to ti ni ilọsiwaju ati awọn ofin hihan.','Manage plugin permission settings.'=>'Ṣakoso awọn eto aṣẹ afikun.','Bypass content restrictions for editorial workflows.'=>'Bọ awọn ihamọ akoonu fun awọn iṣẹ ṣiṣatunkọ.','Set custom post statuses for content items.'=>'Ṣeto awọn ipo ifiweranṣẹ aṣa fun awọn nkan akoonu.','Force Quick Edit access when restrictions would otherwise block it.'=>'Mú iraye si Ṣatunkọ Yara ṣiṣẹ nigbati awọn ihamọ yoo dẹkun rẹ.','Roles & Groups'=>'Ipa & Awọn Ẹgbẹ','Assign or change role assignments for users.'=>'Yipada tabi yi awọn aṣẹ ipa fun awọn olumulo.','Create new permission groups.'=>'Ṣẹda awọn ẹgbẹ aṣẹ tuntun.','Edit existing permission groups.'=>'Ṣatunkọ awọn ẹgbẹ aṣẹ to wa.','Delete permission groups.'=>'Pa awọn ẹgbẹ aṣẹ run.','Add or remove members from permission groups.'=>'Fi awọn ọmọ ẹgbẹ kun tabi yọ wọn kuro ninu awọn ẹgbẹ aṣẹ.','Create network-wide permission groups in multisite.'=>'Ṣẹda awọn ẹgbẹ aṣẹ ni gbogbo nẹtiwọọki ni multisite.','Manage members of network-wide permission groups.'=>'Ṣakoso awọn ọmọ ẹgbẹ ti awọn ẹgbẹ aṣẹ nẹtiwọọki.','Exception Management'=>'Iṣakoso Aiyede','Set per-item association exceptions.'=>'Ṣeto awọn aiyede asopọ fun ọkọọkan.','Set per-item edit exceptions.'=>'Ṣeto awọn aiyede ṣiṣatunkọ fun ọkọọkan.','Set per-item read exceptions.'=>'Ṣeto awọn aiyede kika fun ọkọọkan.','Set per-item revision exceptions.'=>'Ṣeto awọn aiyede atunṣe fun ọkọọkan.','Set taxonomy term assignment exceptions.'=>'Ṣeto awọn aiyede asignment ọrọ taxonomy.','Set taxonomy term association exceptions.'=>'Ṣeto awọn aiyede asopọ ọrọ taxonomy.','Set taxonomy term management exceptions.'=>'Ṣeto awọn aiyede iṣakoso ọrọ taxonomy.','Content Associations'=>'Asopọ Akọkọ','Associate users or groups with any page.'=>'So awọn olumulo tabi awọn ẹgbẹ pọ pẹlu eyikeyi oju-iwe.','Define and apply custom post statuses.'=>'Ṣalaye ki o si lo awọn ipo ifiweranṣẹ aṣa.','Define custom privacy policies for content.'=>'Ṣalaye awọn ilana aṣiri aṣa fun akoonu.','Moderate any item regardless of authorship.'=>'Ṣakoso eyikeyi nkan laibikita onkọwe.','Media & Misc'=>'Media & Misc','Edit attachments uploaded by the current user.'=>'Ṣatunkọ awọn asopọ ti a gbe wọle nipasẹ olumulo lọwọlọwọ.','List unattached files uploaded by other users.'=>'Atokọ awọn faili ti ko ni asopọ ti a gbe wọle nipasẹ awọn olumulo miiran.','List all media library files.'=>'Atokọ gbogbo awọn faili ile-ikawe media.','Exempt user from edit-circle restrictions.'=>'Yọ olumulo kuro ninu awọn idiwọ iyika ṣiṣatunkọ.','Exempt user from read-circle restrictions.'=>'Yọ olumulo kuro ninu awọn idiwọ iyika kika.','see %1$sRole Usage%2$s: "Pattern Roles"'=>'wo %1$sIṣeduro ipa%2$s: "Awọn ipa àpẹẹrẹ"','activate %1$sAdvanced settings%2$s, see Role Usage'=>'mu %1$sIṣeto to ti ni ilọsiwaju%2$s ṣiṣẹ, wo Ipa Lilo','"Posts" capabilities selected here also define type-specific role assignment for Permission Groups%s.'=>'"Posts" awọn agbara ti a yan nibi tun ṣe alaye ipin ipa pato fun Awọn Ẹgbẹ Iwe-aṣẹ%s.','"Posts" capabilities selected here also define type-specific role assignment for Permit Groups%s.'=>'"Posts" awọn agbara ti a yan nibi tun ṣe alaye ipin ipa pato fun Awọn Ẹgbẹ Iwe-aṣẹ%s.','Capabilities for custom statuses can be manually added here. (See %sPermissions > Post Statuses%s for applicable names). %sSupplemental status-specific roles%s are usually more convenient, though.'=>'Awọn agbara fun awọn ipo aṣa le ṣee fi kun ni ọwọ nibi. (Wo %sAwọn igbanilaaye > Awọn ipo Ifiweranṣẹ%s fun awọn orukọ to wulo). %sAwọn ipa afikun pato ipo%s jẹ igbagbogbo rọrun diẹ sii, sibẹsibẹ.','Capabilities for custom statuses can be manually added here. Or activate the PP Custom Post Statuses extension to assign status-specific supplemental roles.'=>'Awọn agbara fun awọn ipo aṣa le ṣee fi kun ni ọwọ nibi. Tabi mu ṣiṣẹ afikun PP Awọn ipo Ifiweranṣẹ aṣa lati yan awọn ipa afikun pato ipo.','Capabilities for custom statuses can be manually added to a role here (see Conditions > Status > Capability Mapping for applicable names). However, it is usually more convenient to use Permit Groups to assign a supplemental status-specific role.'=>'Awọn agbara fun awọn ipo aṣa le ṣee fi kun ni ọwọ si ipa nibi (wo Awọn ipo > Ipo > Mappin Agbara fun awọn orukọ ti o wulo). Sibẹsibẹ, o maa n rọrun lati lo Awọn Ẹgbẹ Iwe-aṣẹ lati yan ipa afikun ti o ni ibatan si ipo.','Unique Post Type Capabilities'=>'Awọn agbara iru ifiweranṣẹ alailẹgbẹ','Allow post type permissions to be controlled separately from other areas of WordPress. %1$sFind out more.%2$s'=>'Gba laaye awọn igbanilaaye iru ifiweranṣẹ lati ṣakoso ni iyatọ lati awọn agbegbe miiran ti WordPress. %1$sṢawari diẹ sii.%2$s','Use the "Create" capability for selected post types'=>'Lo agbara "Ṣẹda" fun awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ ti a yan','This will cause a new capability to be required for creating posts, and enable a checkbox column here for role assignments. Normally, post creation is controlled by the "Edit" capability.'=>'Eyi yóò fa kí a nilo iṣẹ́ tuntun fún ṣiṣàkóso ìkànnì, àti kí o jẹ́ kí àkójọ aṣayan ṣíṣe níhìn-ín fún ìpinnu ipa. Ní àtẹ̀yìnwá, ṣiṣàkóso ìkànnì ni a n ṣakoso nipasẹ iṣẹ́ "Ṣatunkọ".','Update'=>'Imudojuiwọn','Unique Taxonomy Capabilities'=>'Awọn agbara taxonomy alailẹgbẹ','Allow taxonomy permissions to be controlled separately from other areas of WordPress.'=>'Gba laaye awọn igbanilaaye taxonomy lati ṣakoso ni iyatọ lati awọn agbegbe miiran ti WordPress.','Detailed Taxonomy Capabilities'=>'Agbara Taxonomy Alaye','Allow "Edit", "Delete" and "Assign" capabilities separately from the "Manage" capability.'=>'Gba laaye "Ṣatunkọ", "Pa" ati "Yàn" awọn agbara ni iyatọ lati agbara "Ṣakoso".','Login Redirect'=>'Ìtẹ́numọ́ Wọlé','Logout Redirect'=>'Ìtẹ́numọ́ Sọkalẹ','Registration Redirect'=>'Itọnisọna Iforukọsilẹ','First Login Redirect'=>'Ibi ìkànsí àkọ́kọ́','Enter the URL users in this role should be redirected to after login.'=>'Tẹ URL ti awọn olumulo ninu ipa yii yẹ ki o yipada si lẹhin wọle.','Enter the URL users in this role should be redirected to after logout.'=>'Tẹ URL ti awọn olumulo ninu ipa yii yẹ ki o yipada si lẹhin jade.','Enter the URL users in this role should be redirected to after registration.'=>'Tẹ URL ti awọn olumulo ninu ipa yii yẹ ki o yipada si lẹhin iforukọsilẹ.','Enter the URL users in this role should be redirected to after their first login.'=>'Tẹ URL ti awọn olumulo ninu ipa yii yẹ ki o tọka si lẹhin igbasilẹ akọkọ wọn.','%s Redirects'=>'%s Awọn Itọsọna','Save Changes'=>'Fipamọ Awọn ayipada','Redirect users to the URL they were viewing before login.'=>'Tọka awọn olumulo si URL ti wọn n wo ṣaaju ki wọn to wọle.','Redirect users to a specified URL.'=>'Tọka awọn olumulo si URL kan ti a ṣalaye.','Enter the relative path only without domain for login redirect.'=>'Tẹ ọna ti o ni ibatan nikan laisi agbegbe fun atunṣe wọle.','You must enter the Login Redirect URL.'=>'Iwọ gbọdọ tẹ URL Atunṣe Iwọle.','Enter the relative path only without domain for logout redirect.'=>'Tẹ ọna ti o ni ibatan nikan laisi agbegbe fun atunṣe jade.','Redirect Features allows you to redirect users in a role after Registration, Login or Logout.'=>'Awọn ẹya itọnisọna n gba ọ laaye lati tọka awọn olumulo ni ipa lẹhin Iforukọsilẹ, Wọle tabi Jade.','How to use Redirect Features'=>'Bawo ni lati lo Awọn ẹya Itọsọna','You do not have sufficient permissions to perform this action.'=>'Iwọ ko ni awọn aṣẹ to peye lati ṣe iṣe yii.','Your link has expired, refresh the page and try again.'=>'Asopọ rẹ ti pari, tun ṣe oju-iwe naa ki o si gbiyanju lẹẹkansi.','Missing parameters, refresh the page and try again.'=>'Àwọn àkọsílẹ̀ tí o ṣòfò, tún oju-iwe naa ṣe àtúnṣe ki o si gbìmọ̀ lẹ́ẹ̀kansi.','Invalid role name entry: %s'=>'Iforukọsilẹ orukọ ipa ti ko tọ: %s','The role "%s" already exists. Please choose a different name.'=>'Iṣẹ́ "%s" ti wà títẹ̀sí. Jọ̀wọ́ yan orúkọ míràn.','Something went wrong, the system wasn\'t able to create the role, refresh the page and try again.'=>'Nkan kan ṣẹlẹ, eto naa ko le ṣẹda ipa, tun ṣe igbasilẹ oju-iwe naa ki o si gbiyanju lẹẹkansi.','The new role %s was created successfully.'=>'Iṣẹ́ tuntun %s ti dáaṣẹ́ pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí.','%s role updated successfully.'=>'%s ipa ti ni imudojuiwọn ni aṣeyọri.','Cannot delete default role. You <a href="%s">have to change it first</a>.'=>'Ko le paarẹ ipa aiyipada. Iwọ <a href="%s">ni lati yi i pada akọkọ</a>.','Deleting a system role is not allowed.'=>'Ko gba laaye lati pa iṣẹ eto kan.','%1$d users moved to default role %2$s.'=>'%1$d awọn olumulo ti gbe lọ si ipa aiyipada %2$s.','The role %1$s was successfully deleted. %2$s'=>'Iṣẹ́ %1$s ti parí pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí. %2$s','The selected %1$s roles were successfully deleted. %2$s'=>'Àwọn iṣẹ́ %1$s tí a yàn ti parí pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí. %2$s','The role could not be deleted.'=>'Iṣẹ́ náà kò le parí.','The role %1$s was successfully hidden.'=>'Iṣẹ́ %1$s ti farapamọ́ pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí.','The role %1$s was successfully unhidden.'=>'Iṣẹ́ %1$s ti ṣí pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí.','WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce','Gutenberg editor'=>'Onítẹ̀nà Gutenberg','Classic editor'=>'Onkọwe Ibi pataki','Role Slug'=>'Slug Iṣẹ','The "slug" is the URL-friendly version of the role. It is usually all lowercase and contains only letters, numbers and underscores.'=>'“slug” ni ẹya ti o friendly URL ti ipa. O maa n jẹ gbogbo lẹta kekere ati pe o ni awọn lẹta, awọn nọmba ati awọn abawọn nikan.','Block Login'=>'Dena Wọle','Block users in this role from logging into the site.'=>'Dena awọn olumulo ni ipa yii lati wọle si aaye naa.','Block Dashboard Access'=>'Dena Iraye si Dashboard','Block users in this role from accessing admin area.'=>'Dena awọn olumulo ninu ipa yii lati ni iraye si agbegbe alakoso.','Role Level'=>'Ipele Iṣẹ','Each user role has a level from 0 to 10. The Subscriber role defaults to the lowest level (0). The Administrator role defaults to level 10.'=>'Gbogbo iṣẹ olumulo ni ipele lati 0 si 10. Iṣẹ Alabapin ni ipele ti o kere julọ (0). Iṣẹ Alakoso ni ipele 10.','Delete role'=>'Pa iṣẹ','Deleting this role will completely remove it from database and is irrecoverable.'=>'Pipa iṣẹ yii yoo yọkuro rẹ patapata lati inu ibi ipamọ data ati pe ko le gba pada.','Disable Code Editor'=>'Pa Olùkọ́ Kóòdù mọ́lẹ̀','Disable the "Code editor" option for the Gutenberg block editor.'=>'Pa aṣayan "Olùkọ́ Kóòdù" mọ́lẹ̀ fun olùkọ́ bulọọki Gutenberg.','Control Allowed Editors'=>'Ṣakoso Awọn Onkọwe ti a Gba laaye','Select the allowed editor options for users in this role.'=>'Yan awọn aṣayan olootu ti a gba laaye fun awọn olumulo ni ipa yii.','Disable WooCommerce admin restrictions'=>'Pa awọn ihamọ alakoso WooCommerce mọ́lẹ̀','By default, WooCommerce prevents most users from accessing the WordPress admin area. When enabled, this setting will remove those restrictions for this role. %1s Click here for more details. %2s'=>'Nipa aiyipada, WooCommerce n dena ọpọlọpọ awọn olumulo lati wọle si agbegbe iṣakoso WordPress. Nigbati o ba mu ṣiṣẹ, eto yii yoo yọ awọn ihamọ wọnyẹn fun ipa yii. %1s Tẹ nibi fun alaye diẹ sii. %2s','Slug already exists'=>'Slug ti wa tẹlẹ','Select allowed editor'=>'Yan olootu ti a gba laaye','You must select at least one editor for the role when managing allowed editor.'=>'Iwọ gbọdọ yan o kere ju olootu kan fun ipa nigbati o ba n ṣakoso olootu ti a gba laaye.','Select %s'=>'Yan %s','Read more on Role Level.'=>'Ka siwaju lori Ipele Ipa.','Are you sure you want to delete this role?'=>'Ṣe o dajudaju pe o fẹ pa ipa yii?','%s role copied. Please click the "Create Role" button to create this new role.'=>'%s ipa ti daakọ. Jowo tẹ bọtini "Ṣẹda Ipa" lati ṣẹda ipa tuntun yii.','Edit Role: %s'=>'Ṣatunkọ Iṣẹ: %s','Copy Role'=>'Da Ẹka','Create New Role'=>'Ṣẹda Ẹka Tuntun','All Roles'=>'Gbogbo Awọn ipa','These can be edited on the %1s Capabilities screen %2s'=>'Àwọn wọ̀nyí le ṣe àtúnṣe ní iboju %1s Àǹfààní %2s','Load More'=>'Gbe Ẹlẹkẹta Ọpọ','Load Less'=>'Gbe Ẹlẹkẹta Kéré','All %s'=>'Gbogbo %s','Mine %s'=>'Ti mi %s','Has Users %s'=>'Ni Awọn olumulo %s','No Users %s'=>'Kò sí Àwọn Olùṣàkóso %s','Editable %s'=>'Ẹ̀dá %s','Uneditable %s'=>'Ko le satunkọ %s','System %s'=>'Eto %s','Copy'=>'Daakọ','(non-editable role)'=>'(ipa ti ko le yipada)','Unhide'=>'Ṣii','Your Role'=>'Ipa Rẹ','WordPress Core'=>'WordPress Core','Search Roles'=>'Wa Awọn ipa','Multiples roles on "Add New User" screen'=>'Iṣẹ pupọ lori iboju "Fikun-un Olumulo Tuntun"','This allows you to assign a new user to multiples roles.'=>'Èyí gba ọ laaye láti yàn olumulo tuntun sí ọpọlọpọ awọn iṣẹ́.','Multiples roles on "User Edit" screen'=>'Iṣẹ pupọ lori iboju "Ṣatunkọ Olumulo"','This allows you to assign an existing user to multiple roles.'=>'Èyí gba ọ laaye láti yàn olumulo to wà sí ọpọlọpọ awọn iṣẹ́.','Set login redirect cookie'=>'Ṣeto kukisi gbigbe oju-iwe wọle','Use cookie to determine pages users were viewing before login. This is useful when login redirect is not working correctly due to wp_get_referer() limitation.'=>'Lo kuki lati pinnu awọn oju-iwe ti awọn olumulo n wo ṣaaju ki wọn to wọle. Eyi jẹ wulo nigbati atunṣe wiwọle ko ṣiṣẹ daradara nitori idiwọ wp_get_referer().','Show private post types'=>'Fi awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ ikọkọ han','This will show all post types on the "Capabilities" screen, even ones normally hidden in the WordPress admin area.'=>'Eyi yóò fi hàn gbogbo irú ìkànnì lori iboju "Iṣẹ́", paapaa awọn tí a n dènà ní àgbègbè adarí WordPress.','Show private taxonomies'=>'Fi awọn taxonomies ikọkọ han','This will show all taxonomies on the "Capabilities" screen, even ones normally hidden in the WordPress admin area.'=>'Eyi yóò fi hàn gbogbo ìtòsọ́na lori iboju "Iṣẹ́", paapaa awọn tí a n dènà ní àgbègbè adarí WordPress.','Show all post types on the "Editor Features" screen, even ones normally hidden in the WordPress admin area.'=>'Fi gbogbo awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ han lori iboju "Awọn ẹya Editọ", paapaa awọn ti a maa n pa mọ ni agbegbe alakoso WordPress.','Enable Classic Editor tab'=>'Mú taabu Akọwe Classic ṣiṣẹ','Always show the Classic Editor tab in "Editor Features" screen.'=>'Ma ṣe afihan taabu Ẹdá Classic nigbagbogbo ninu iboju "Awọn ẹya Ẹdá".','Admin Bar modification'=>'Iyipada Bar Alakoso','When testing, display a caption and return link in the Admin Bar.'=>'Nígbà tí a bá n danwò, fi akọle kan hàn àti ìjápọ̀ padà nínú Ọgá Bar.','Admin Bar search'=>'Ìwádìí Bar Alakoso','Add option to search and user testing in the Admin Bar.'=>'Ṣe afikun aṣayan lati wa ati idanwo olumulo ni Admin Bar.','Front End footer notice'=>'Ìkìlọ̀ ẹsẹ́ iwaju','When testing, display a return link in the front end footer.'=>'Nígbà tí a bá n danwò, fi ìjápọ̀ padà hàn nínú ẹsẹ́ iwaju.','Exclude role from User Testing'=>'Yọ ipa kuro ninu Iṣeduro Awọn olumulo','Select roles...'=>'Yan awọn ipa...','Exclude users in selected roles from User Testing.'=>'Yọ awọn olumulo ninu awọn ipa ti a yan kuro ninu Iṣeduro Awọn olumulo.','Automatically refresh profile elements'=>'Tun awọn eroja profaili laifọwọyi','Always try to automatically find profile elements. This may cause temporary issues when updating user roles that do not have access to the WordPress admin area.'=>'Maṣe gbiyanju lati wa awọn eroja profaili laifọwọyi nigbagbogbo. Eyi le fa awọn iṣoro igba diẹ nigbati o ba n ṣe imudojuiwọn awọn ipa olumulo ti ko ni iraye si agbegbe iṣakoso WordPress.','Capabilities Settings'=>'Awọn Eto Agbara','Search user...'=>'Wa olumulo...','Search'=>'Wa','No results found.'=>'Kò sí abajade tí a rí.','Permission denied.'=>'Iṣẹ-iyọọda ti kọ.','Test user'=>'Dáhùn olumulo','Test this user'=>'Dáhùn olumulo yi','Testing: '=>'Testing: ','%1$sReturn to Administrator view%2$s'=>'%1$sPadà si iwo Alakoso%2$s','Testing as user: %1$s. %2$sReturn to Administrator view%3$s'=>'Testing gẹgẹ bi olumulo: %1$s. %2$sPade pada si wiwo Olùdarí%3$s','Unable to retrieve user data.'=>'Ko le gba data olumulo.']];